## BlOCK a specific IP address for ssh
ubuntu@ip-172-31-42-104:~$ sudo iptables -I INPUT -s 172.31.42.104 -p tcp --dport ssh -j REJECT

Acccess from your ssh server from your mobile using termux
1.check ssh is working not 
   $ ssh
2. if  there is no ssh install it by 
   $ pkg install openssh
3. them ssh from your mobile
   $ ssh ubuntu@172.31.42.104
   
   
